The Porsche Design Tower at 18555 Collins Ave in Sunny Isles Beach, FL 33160 offers valet parking services to its residents and guests. Our valet parking policy aims to provide a convenient and efficient parking experience while ensuring the safety and security of vehicles entrusted to us.

Upon arrival at the Porsche Design Tower, guests and residents can drive up to the designated valet parking area located at the front entrance. Our professional valet staff will be readily available to assist with the parking process. 

To ensure a smooth and organized procedure, valet attendants will request the necessary information from the vehicle owner, including their name, contact number, and the duration of the parking required. This information will be recorded and securely stored for reference.

After retrieving the necessary details, the valet attendant will carefully park the vehicle in the designated parking area assigned to the Porsche Design Tower. We prioritize safe parking practices, ensuring that vehicles are placed in designated spots that maximize space and minimize the risk of damage or accidents.

When the vehicle owner is ready to depart, they can request their vehicle from the valet attendant. The owner will need to present the corresponding valet ticket provided at the time of drop-off. This ticket serves as proof of ownership and allows us to ensure that the vehicle is returned to the correct owner.

Throughout the parking process, the Porsche Design Tower takes great care in safeguarding the vehicles entrusted to our valet service. Our parking area is monitored by advanced surveillance systems and our attendants are trained to handle vehicles with the utmost professionalism and respect.

Please note that the Porsche Design Tower assumes no responsibility for personal belongings left inside the vehicles. It is recommended that owners remove any valuable items from their vehicles before handing them over to the valet attendant.

At the Porsche Design Tower, we strive to provide exceptional valet parking services that align with our commitment to excellence. We appreciate your cooperation and look forward to ensuring a pleasant and secure parking experience for all our residents and guests.
